msgstr "使用这个主题来帮助您通过 Windows PowerShell 管理 Windows 和 Windows Server 技术。"

msgid "# New-ClusterFaultDomain"
msgstr "# 新集群故障域（New-ClusterFaultDomain）"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Creates a fault domain in the cluster."
msgstr "在集群中创建一个故障域。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The `New-ClusterFaultDomain` cmdlet creates a fault domain in the cluster. Additionally, you can\n"
"specify the relationship between the fault domains when they are created."
msgstr ""
"`New-ClusterFaultDomain` cmdlet 用于在集群中创建故障域。此外，在创建故障域时，您还可以指定这些故障域之间的关系。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid ""
"### Example 1: Create a cluster fault domain in an existing fault domain"
msgstr "### 示例 1：在现有的故障域中创建一个集群故障域"

msgid ""
"This command creates a cluster fault domain of type Rack named `Rack1` in the existing fault domain\n"
"named `Site001`."
msgstr "此命令在现有的故障域“Site001”中创建一个类型为“Rack”的集群故障域，命名为“Rack1”。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that take a long time to\n"
"complete."
msgstr "以后台作业的方式运行该cmdlet。使用此参数来执行那些需要较长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command\n"
"prompt. You can continue to work in the session while the job completes. To manage the job, use the\n"
"`*-Job` cmdlets. To get the job results, use the\n"
"[Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该cmdlet会立即返回一个表示该作业的对象，随后会显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在该会话中工作。要管理该作业，请使用`*-Job`系列的cmdlets；要获取作业结果，请使用[Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about Windows PowerShell background jobs, see\n"
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 Windows PowerShell 后台任务的更多信息，请参阅 "
"[关于任务（about_Jobs）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer. Enter a computer name or a session\n"
"object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)\n"
"or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet. The default is the\n"
"current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该cmdlet。可以输入一个计算机名称，或者输入一个会话对象（例如[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)或[Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) "
"cmdlet的输出结果）。默认情况下，该cmdlet会在本地计算机的当前会话中运行。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the description of the cluster fault domain that this cmdlet "
"creates."
msgstr "指定此cmdlet创建的集群故障域的描述信息。"

msgid "Specifies the name of the fault domain."
msgstr "指定故障域的名称。"

msgid "Specifies the type of the fault domain that this cmdlet creates."
msgstr "指定此cmdlet创建的故障域的类型。"

msgid "The acceptable values for this parameter are:"
msgstr "此参数的可接受值为："

msgid ""
"Any flags that need to be passed in when creating the cluster fault domain."
msgstr "在创建集群故障域时需要传递的任何标志（flags）。"

msgid ""
"A string describing the location of the cluster fault domain that will be "
"created."
msgstr "一段用于描述将要创建的集群故障域位置的字符串。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the name of the cluster fault domain that this cmdlet creates."
msgstr "指定此cmdlet创建的集群故障域的名称。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet. If\n"
"this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then Windows PowerShell calculates an\n"
"optimum throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the\n"
"computer. The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the\n"
"computer."
msgstr ""
"指定可以同时运行的 cmdlet 操作的最大数量。如果省略此参数或输入值 `0`，则 Windows PowerShell 会根据计算机上正在运行的 "
"CIM cmdlet 的数量来计算该 cmdlet 的最佳限制值（即并发操作的数量）。此限制仅适用于当前运行的 "
"cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

msgid "### CommonParameters"
msgstr "### CommonParameters"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet supports the common parameters: -Debug, -ErrorAction, -ErrorVariable,\n"
"-InformationAction, -InformationVariable, -OutVariable, -OutBuffer, -PipelineVariable, -Verbose,\n"
"-WarningAction, and -WarningVariable. For more information, see\n"
"[about_CommonParameters](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)."
msgstr ""
"此 cmdlet "
"支持以下常见参数：-Debug、-ErrorAction、-ErrorVariable、-InformationAction、-OutputVariable、-OutBuffer、-PipelineVariable、-Verbose、-WarningAction"
" 和 -WarningVariable。有关更多信息，请参阅 "
"[about_CommonParameters](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113216)。"

